use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3612324\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_3612324\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104cdy1665702648580.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cdy1665702648580.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/cdy1665702648580.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"cdy1665702648580\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      TakeFocus\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether the OCX control gets focus so that the user does not need to click the control first. <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> (default) or <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cdy1665702648580__p_d108008e1_d108009e1_d108010e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>TakeFocus<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cdy1665702648580__table_d12728e1_d12729e1_d12730e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cdy1665702648580__table_d12728e1_d12729e1_d12730e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"cdy1665702648580__table_d12728e1_d12729e1_d12730e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cdy1665702648580__table_d12728e1_d12729e1_d12730e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> (true)</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cdy1665702648580__table_d12728e1_d12729e1_d12730e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The focus is first set to the OCX container window and then to the control itself.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cdy1665702648580__table_d12728e1_d12729e1_d12730e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"cdy1665702648580__table_d12728e1_d12729e1_d12730e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The focus is set to the OCX container window, not to the control.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cdy1665702648580__section_y41_mk2_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1185564e139\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"cdy1665702648580__table_d11987e1_d11988e1_d11989e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dynamic?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Yes</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Supported in Grid?</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">No</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Dependencies:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">None</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cdy1665702648580__section_zvz_mk2_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1185564e185\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cdy1665702648580__p_d108017e1_d108018e1_d108019e1\">In some cases, the default value causes the control\n            to work incorrectly, and it only works after the user has activated it with a mouse\n            click. In this case, set  TakeFocus to\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cdy1665702648580__section_zyc_4k2_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1185564e199\">Using in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"cdy1665702648580__p_d108023e1_d108024e1_d108025e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$properties</span> or\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$fieldproperties</span> to set or get the property and its value. For\n            more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zie1665702558978.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zie1665702558978.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of a field.\">$properties</a> and <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aud1705998763272.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1705998763272.html\" title=\"Return or set the current widget properties of an instance of a field.\">$fieldproperties</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"cdy1665702648580__pre_tvm_pk2_1xb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD) = \"TakeFocus=False\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"cdy1665702648580__section_vpq_pk2_1xb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1185564e232\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vvo1665702647716.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vvo1665702647716.html\" title=\"The uOcxContainer widget embeds a Microsoft OCX control into a form component, and maps OCX properties and OCX events to fields and triggers. You can use ProcScript to activate OCX methods and let the OCX control activate widget triggers to respond to OCX events.\">uOcxContainer (OcxContainer)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612324\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612324\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "TakeFocus Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 TakeFocus Determines whether the OCX control gets focus so that the user does not need to click the control first. True (default) or False . \" TakeFocus = True | False \" Value Description True (true) The focus is first set to the OCX container window and then to the control itself. False The focus is set to the OCX container window, not to the control. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: None Description In some cases, the default value causes the control to work incorrectly, and it only works after the user has activated it with a mouse click. In this case, set TakeFocus to False . Using in ProcScript You can use $properties or $fieldproperties to set or get the property and its value. For more information, see $properties and $fieldproperties . $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"TakeFocus=False\" Copy Applies To uOcxContainer (OcxContainer) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}